data.description: Looking for a beautifully kept 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home in the West Killeen area with a covered front porch, covered back patio, in-ground irrigation system, and privacy fence with private backyard?   Then this might be the home for you!  AND, as an added bonus, the home has a brand new, architectural-style shingle roof that comes with a lifetime product warranty and 10 year labor warranty that is backed by the manufacturer and will transfer to the lucky new owner.  This stunning home offers upgrades such as high ceilings, large windows with faux wood blinds throughout, ceiling fans in every bedroom and family room, granite kitchen countertops with a breakfast bar, updated stainless steel appliances, and a jacuzzi tub.  Nearby Fort Hood/Fort Cavazos is only a short drive away.  Centrally located between Austin and Waco, on a quiet, dead-end street in the desirable neighborhood of Goodnight Ranch (just off of Bunny Trail), with close access to shopping, grocery stores, restaurants, parks and quick access to 195. This gorgeous home will sell fast.  Be sure to schedule your showing today!
